BUTTONS

 - Engine / World Operations

   F1            : fullscreen
                   (leaks mem, old crufty X code needs replacement)

   F2            : fps toggle
                   (console)

   F3            : decrease Minimum Critters
   F4            : increase Minimum Critters

   F7            : insert Adam

   F11           : load all critters from "~/.critterding/load" directory
   F12           : save all critters into "~/.critterding/save/(time)" directory

   Insert        : toggle critter vision

 - Camera Operations

   Arrow Up      : move forward
   Arrow Down    : move backward
   Arrow Left    : strafe left
   Arrow Right   : strafe right
   Home          : move up
   End           : move down
   NumKey 2      : look up
   NumKey 8      : look down
   NumKey 4      : look left
   NumKey 6      : look right

TERMINOLOGY

 - Adam
      : new (100% random) critter

 - Adam Distance (ad)
      : mutations since adam

